-- Nova Rises to Month High on Supply Deal With Asian Manufacturer
-- B y   S h o s h a n n a   S o l o m o n
-- 2012-06-20T11:13:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-20/nova-rises-to-month-high-on-supply-deal-with-asian-manufacturer.html
Nova Measuring Instruments Ltd. (NVMI) 
climbed to the highest in more than a month after the developer
of monitoring systems for the semiconductor industry said it
will supply its T600 metrology tool to an Asian manufacturer.  The  shares  gained 3.6 percent to 33.15 shekels, the highest
intraday level since May 7, at 1:32 p.m. in  Tel Aviv .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shoshanna Solomon in Tel Aviv at 
 ssolomon22@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
